export: sshkey_digitalocean_list, sshkey_digitalocean_get, sshkey_create, sshkey_digitalocean_modifications, sshkey_digitalocean_delete
---
Name: sshkey_digitalocean_list
Description: Call this tool to list, get or get_by id ssh keys in digitalocean
Tools: sshkeys_list from github.com/cloudnautique/digitalocean/sshkeys

Use the appropriate tools to service the request and return the results
---
Name: sshkey_digitalocean_get
Description: Call this tool to list, get or get_by id ssh keys in digitalocean
Tools: sshkeys_get_by_id from github.com/cloudnautique/digitalocean/sshkeys
args: key_id: the ID of the key

Use the appropriate tools to service the request and return the results
---
Name: sshkey_create
Description: Call this to create a new sshkey in the workspace
Tools: sys.exec?
Args: keyname: Name of the keyfile

#!/usr/bin/env bash
if [ ! -f "${GPTSCRIPT_WORKSPACE_DIR}/${keyname}" ]; then
    ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -N '' -f ${GPTSCRIPT_WORKSPACE_DIR}/${keyname}
fi
---
